<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Student Services</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <style>
    .services-images {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .services-images img {
      width: calc(50% - 10px);
      max-width: 600px;
      height: 350px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .services-images img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .services-images img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 220px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .services-images img {
        height: 180px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="content">
  <h1>Student Services</h1>
  <hr>
  <p>Student Services form the backbone of a supportive educational environment. They are designed to ensure that every learner has access to the resources, guidance, and opportunities needed to thrive academically, socially, and personally. By addressing diverse student needs, these services help create a holistic learning experience that extends beyond the classroom.<br>
  <hr>
  🎓 Academic Support<br>
  -  Tutoring and Mentoring: One-on-one or group sessions to strengthen subject knowledge.<br>
  -  Advising: Guidance on course selection, study plans, and academic progression.<br>
  -  Workshops: Training in study skills, time management, and exam preparation.<br>
  <hr>
  💼 Career Development<br>
  -  Career Counseling: Personalized advice to align education with career goals.<br>
  -  Internships & Placements: Opportunities to gain real-world experience.<br>
  -  Skill Building: Resume writing, interview preparation, and networking events.<br>
  <hr>
  🧘 Counseling & Wellness<br>
  -  Mental Health Services: Confidential counseling and therapy sessions.<br>
  -  Wellness Programs: Stress management, mindfulness, and fitness activities.<br>
  -  Peer Support Groups: Safe spaces for sharing experiences and building resilience.<br>
  <hr>
  💰 Financial Aid & Scholarships<br>
  -  Scholarship Guidance: Information on merit-based and need-based awards.<br>
  -  Financial Aid Assistance: Help with applications for grants and loans.<br>
  -  Budgeting Workshops: Training to manage personal finances effectively.<br>
  <hr>
  🌍 Student Life & Engagement<br>
  -  Clubs & Societies: Opportunities to join cultural, academic, and recreational groups.<br>
  -  Events & Activities: Festivals, competitions, and leadership programs.<br>
  -  Sports & Recreation: Facilities and coaching for physical development.<br>
  <hr>
  ♿ Accessibility & Inclusion<br>
  -  Support for Students with Disabilities: Assistive technologies, accommodations, and specialized counseling.<br>
  -  Inclusive Programs: Initiatives to celebrate diversity and promote equal opportunities.<br>
  -  Awareness Campaigns: Activities to foster empathy and inclusivity on campus.<br>
  <hr>
  </p>

